{"tid":262734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(裝左薩德都無用) 美NASA揭 中國一氧化碳圍攻日韓台","createTime":"2017-05-29T12:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T14:57:08.000Z","uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a363117b4d05fd73b07fb7dadb94ca586198322","tid":262734,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T12:39:11.000Z","msg":"中國空氣污染問題嚴峻，輸出的污染物不僅霧霾及沙塵。美國太空總署（NASA）的監測發現，今年1月中至3月，中國的一氧化碳不斷向東亞地區擴散，受影響的包括台灣、日本及南韓等地。 <br />\n<br />\n根據美國太空總署（NASA）的Geos-5地球觀測系統模擬片，中國的一氧化碳濃度在今年1月15日至3月1日間，冠絕東亞地區，並且不斷向台灣、日本、南韓等地。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static01.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1820000/1824460/236_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1820000%2F1824460%2F236_1024.png&h=7ca46b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共:「韓國仔以為裝左薩德, 我就無佢辦法, 睇下我既大絕」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb28e61cb16cd07f3f432aa43612ee03f7066d3c","tid":262734,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a15c31bdb25842828a2f642e5eee689b737ca4fb","tid":262734,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"如果打ww3，支共用氣象"},{"pid":"57ff793e92604adfa02a89408a834c211e68a267","tid":262734,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"如果打ww3，支共用氣象武器有冇機會一统東亞？"},{"pid":"90b5015bdc5e37178d5ede34ea594084a3f9ac53","tid":262734,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:31:57.000Z","msg":"燒你炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0294e692734d70ec859ab31115ef3fbf5004c93e","tid":262734,"uid":18233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:33:32.000Z"